ure is immune to being frightened and gains temporary hit points equal to your spellcasting ability modifier at the start of each of its turns. When the spell ends, the target loses any remaining temporary hit points from this spell.<br>&bull;<b>At Higher Levels:</b> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st.<br>"},{"name":"Tasha's Hideous Laughter","level":1,"castTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","components":{"verbal":true,"somatic":true,"material":"tiny tarts and a feather that is waved in the air"},"classes":["Bard","Wizard"],"school":"Enchantment","duration":"Concentration up to 1 minute","selected":true,"alwaysPrepared":true,"prepared":true,"description":"A creature of your choice that you can see within range perceives everything as hilariously funny and falls into fits of laughter if this spell affects it. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or fall prone, becoming incapacitated and unable to stand up for the duration. A creature with an Intelligence score of 4 or less isn't affected.<br>At the end of each of its turns, and each time it takes damage, the target can make another Wisdom saving throw. The target has advantage on the saving throw if it's triggered by damage. On a success, the spell ends.<br>"}]}],"saves":{"str":0,"dex":1,"con":0,"wis":0,"int":0,"cha":1},"attributes":{"str":9,"dex":14,"con":16,"wis":11,"int":10,"cha":16},"skills":[{"name":"Acrobatics","mult":1,"attribute":"dex"},{"name":"Animal Handling","mult":0,"attribute":"wis"},{"name":"Arcana","mult":1,"attribute":"int"},{"name":"Athletics","mult":0,"attribute":"str"},{"name":"Deception","mult":1,"attribute":"cha"},{"name":"History","mult":0,"attribute":"int"},{"name":"Insight","mult":1,"attribute":"wis"},{"name":"Intimidation","mult":0,"attribute":"cha"},{"name":"Investigation","mult":1,"attribute":"int"},{"name":"Medicine","mult":0,"attribute":"wis"},{"name":"Nature","mult":0,"attri